This Express Service operates on the dates of all Dodger home games, departing from Harbor Gateway Transit Center Bay #9 and running up the Harbor Transitway to Dodger Stadium, beginning 2 Hours before game time and continuing until 45 minutes after the game ends. This is a free service to anyone with a ticket to the game.

This Express Service operates on the dates of all Dodger home games, departing from the West Portal of Historic Union Station and running directly to Dodger Stadium, beginning 90 minutes before game time and continuing until 45 minutes after the game ends. This is a free service to anyone with a ticket to the game.

The express shuttle will operate between the Metro K-Line Downtown Inglewood Station and SoFi Stadium. Shuttle service will run every 5-8 minutes beginning roughly 3 hours before the event begins and ending roughly 1.5 hours after the event concludes. During the event, shuttles will depart SoFi to the Metro K-Line Downtown Inglewood Station as needed. Metro express shuttle service to SoFi Stadium is FREE, but normal fares apply for regular Metro Bus and Rail service and parking fees at Metro Park & Ride lots

The express shuttle will operate between the Metro C-Line Hawthorne/Lennox Station and SoFi Stadium. Shuttle service will run every 5-8 minutes beginning roughly 3 hours before the event begins and ending roughly 1.5 hours after the event concludes. During the event, shuttles will depart SoFi to the Metro C-Line Hawthorne/Lennox Station as needed. Metro express service to SoFi Stadium is FREE, but normal fares apply for regular Metro Bus and Rail service and parking fees at Metro Park & Ride lots
